+/// Size of the bounded channels used to communicate between tasks.
+///
+/// Remote TUI sessions can emit large first-turn bursts (tool output, plan
+/// deltas, reasoning deltas, completions) quickly enough that 128 messages
+/// proves too small for the websocket transport path. Give the local transport
+/// substantially more headroom so transient render stalls do not look like a
+/// permanently slow client.
+pub(crate) const CHANNEL_CAPACITY: usize = 4096;

